title: Gunman kills one and injures three in Jerusalem
content: A member of the Hamas militant group opens fire in the Old City, and is shot dead by Israeli police.

title: Further unrest in Netherlands amid Covid protests
content: Riots erupt in the Netherlands for a second night, with protests also held in Austria and Italy.

title: Video claims to show Peng Shuai at tournament
content: A state media video claims to show her as a guest at a tournament, amid concerns for her wellbeing.

title: Fireworks and chaos as Dutch Covid riots continue
content: Rioters in the Netherlands clashed with police for a second night over new coronavirus measures.

title: Sudan's military to reinstate ousted PM
content: Abdalla Hamdok has been under house arrest since a military coup last month, sparking mass protests.

title: Bear shot dead by 70-year-old hunter in France
content: A female bear roaming with her cubs is killed after attacking and injuring a man, officials say.

content: It is being billed as the most polarising election in decades and comes after divisive mass protests.
